{"tid":1391430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日日運動半個鐘 健康快樂人輕鬆","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:21:43.000Z","uid":77872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9514c7b0175c5a9ea1d4b08d726b8bb0581e4ca","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"全民運動日<br />\n<br />\n香港人生活忙碌，工作壓力大，應多做運動，有益身心。近日社會上出現不同形式的運動。以見及此，我想推介一些平時比較少見的運動，例如棍網球(lacrosse)，近年開始流入香港，漸漸興起。<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/kb9DyjTz8BZ9gK6NA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2Fkb9DyjTz8BZ9gK6NA&h=5f73ff75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n棍網球是一種團體運動，球員利用手上啲棍，將球攻進對方的龍門得分。棍網球的棍有分兩種，分別是進攻的短棍<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/9N39CJdysSkU7Yv58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2F9N39CJdysSkU7Yv58&h=58d67cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和防守的長棍<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/Yr32KWYHFs2we8c19\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FYr32KWYHFs2we8c19&h=dd1e9f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於此項運動難以避免有些肢體碰撞，為了保護自己，所以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打這項運動時必須穿好裝備</span></span></strong> <img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/JiCZYTncdGUpcGMt8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FJiCZYTncdGUpcGMt8&h=6faa4c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在供團體練習棍網球的地方不多，練習場地的供應非常緊張。雖然team work練習是重要，可以個人技術在此項運動也不能忽視的，另外個人練習便不會太受場地所限，只要找到有牆的地方，便能進行wall ball，或者可以在任何地方練習stick skills，同手中的棍打好關係，培養感情，比賽時便能事半功倍。 <img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/pmruhBUapZ1o2bJFA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FpmruhBUapZ1o2bJFA&h=f7f2bb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然個人技術可以在任何地方練習，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>***不過要提醒在有些地方練習是非常危險的，例如警署週邊，千萬不能去那裡附近練習，以免誤傷途人！***</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，仲有一種球類運動叫壘球(soft ball)，其玩法與日本的棒球相近，詳情可參考該運動。做運動最緊要安全，所以大家都要著齊打soft ball的裝備，如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/re1bFnVjhNFETyaE6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2Fre1bFnVjhNFETyaE6&h=8a7fd42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/7tv9ikMVRZLq8Ni4A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2F7tv9ikMVRZLq8Ni4A&h=5acfe95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句，平時練習揈Bat，投球等個人技術時，要注意安全，上齊裝備，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>千萬唔好去警署附近練習，因為真係好危險，以免誤傷途人。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n推介埋最後一樣都係平時比較少見的球類<br />\n運動，曲棍球(Hockey)。玩法同ice hockey類近，裝備如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/pwankygnwFBavw6Z8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FpwankygnwFBavw6Z8&h=fb360c11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人生活實在太繁忙，多做運動身體有益。如果大家想做翻啲比較傳統運動，例如羽毛球、網球、壁球等的話，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>最緊要著齊裝備，揸實球拍，保護自己，以免誤傷他人。</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>千奇千奇唔好係警署附近打波練習，因為真係好危險好危險，有機會誤傷途人、甚至誤傷食飽飯冇嘢做被人拉落街散步的狗隻。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打咩ball，做咩運動都好<br />\n<br />\n緊記五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n撤回612暴動定性<br />\n必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴及元朗暴力事件<br />\n全面落實雙真普選</span></span>"},{"pid":"a19e02a4596962d2154789bd0c0db9367a75e966","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78560ef7ab945d44b7579a203d48fdd7e35fe7f1","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a14d9ccf35af2f2c79105debaef8e7cdaadd7dea","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e90b69b88e9caf02b199c61f4a7a9aaa9e78183e","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eab9378d9e138b1c25c5de51780da0fb2eb1f09b","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9c73582bf14737b264adb7659bde243325808e17","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5ccd18e996cbf893166d5d1a4ba53d95f82935e","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"pusb"},{"pid":"52c5d0c40dead6e921cae0bb6546cafe0ddb254f","tid":1391430,"uid":77872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"push"}]}